title: GETTING THE KNACK OF THE CENSUS TRACT
desc:
This Webinar will describe the history of the Census Tract, its evolution until now, and then finalise by giving a demonstration of how to get data at the Census Tract level in the Census Bureau's American Factfinder tool. 
 Go directly to this link, in order to register in Webex: 
 https://census.webex.com/mw0401lsp13/mywebex/default.do?service=1&siteurl=census&nomenu=false&main_url=%2Fmc0901lsp13%2Fmeetingcenter%2Fdefault.do%3Fsiteurl%3Dcensus%26rnd%3D8973127406%26main_url%3D%252Fmc0901lsp13%252Fe.do%253Fsiteurl%253Dcensus%2526AT%253DMI%2526EventID%253D390533517%2526UID%253D0%2526Host%253DQUhTSwAAAAK6EkAoD0oF-hrmrnF8kpi_Cxl4lmG6ze4pzf2L1UH9HzO3EBf9kRlTpmcg0pLqBVE4Faf0uAyDeogEm_i-ekZi0%2526RG%253D1%2526FrameSet%253D2
